# AgToosa Task Rules

When executing `/agtoosa-task` or any lightweight issue capture, follow `Docs/AgToosa_Task.md` precisely.

On successful completion, print this line verbatim: `✅ Done. Run /agtoosa-status to verify findings cleared.`
